OL,3,CDouble killer Hazel Stewart fails in
OL,4,Cbid to have sentence reduced
OL,6,FDouble murderer Hazel Stewart has
OL,7,Ffailed in her legal bid to have her
OL,8,Fsentence reduced for killing her
OL,9,Fpoliceman husband and the wife of her
OL,10,Fex-lover.
OL,12,FA panel of judges at the Court of
OL,13,FAppeal in Belfast ruled that the
OL,14,Fsentence imposed on Stewart, 62, a
OL,15,Fformer Sunday school teacher, was
OL,16,F"neither wrong nor manifestly
OL,17,Fexcessive".
