OL,3,CDouble killer Hazel Stewart fails in
OL,4,Cbid to have sentence reduced
OL,6,FLady Chief Justice Dame Siobhan Keegan
OL,7,Ftold the court that Stewart's latest
OL,8,Fattempted appeal would have caused
OL,9,F"stress and upset" to the families of
OL,10,Fthose she killed.
OL,12,FStewart's lawyer described the ruling
OL,13,Fas disappointing, but said it "doesn't
OL,14,Fend the quest to highlight that she
OL,15,Fwas a victim of coercive control".
OL,17,FShe is serving a minimum 18 years
OL,18,Fbehind bars for the killing of
OL,19,FConstable Trevor Buchanan, 32, and 31-
OL,20,Fyear-old Lesley Howell, the wife of
OL,21,Fher former lover Colin Howell.
