OL,6,FBoth were found in a fume-filled
OL,7,Fgarage in Castlerock, Co Londonderry,
OL,8,Fin May 1991.
OL,10,FPolice originally believed they had
OL,11,Fdied in a suicide pact, after
OL,12,Fdiscovering that their partners were
OL,13,Fhaving an extra-marital affair.
OL,15,FInstead, they had been drugged and
OL,16,Fmurdered and their bodies arranged to
OL,17,Fmake it look as though they had taken
OL,18,Ftheir own lives.
