OL,6,FNearly two decades passed before
OL,7,Fdentist Howell, 65, confessed to both
OL,8,Fkillings.
OL,10,FHe implicated Stewart and she was
OL,11,Fordered to serve at least 18 years, at
OL,12,Fher trial in 2011.
OL,14,FStewart launched her appeal against
OL,15,Fthe length of her sentence on the
OL,16,Fbasis of fresh psychiatric evidence
OL,17,Fthat suggested she was suffering from
OL,18,Fdepression and post-traumatic stress
OL,19,Fdisorder at the time of the murders
OL,20,Fand had been coercively controlled by
OL,21,FHowell.
