OL,6,FStewart, wearing a pale blue T-shirt
OL,7,Fand a cross necklace, watched the
OL,8,Fcourt of appeal ruling via a videolink
OL,9,Ffrom Hydebank Prison.
OL,11,FDame Siobhan said the fresh
OL,12,Fpsychiatric evidence had been
OL,13,Fpresented "well after the event" and
OL,14,F"places reliance on prison records to
OL,15,Fcontradict the case made by all other
OL,16,Fexperts".
