OL,6,FShe said: "Even if there were any
OL,7,Ftraction in the points now made, which
OL,8,Fwe do not find, the trial judge also
OL,9,Fmade allowance for Howell's control in
OL,10,Fthe sentence he passed.
OL,12,F"No injustice arises in refusing to
OL,13,Freopen this long-concluded appeal on
OL,14,Fthese facts."
OL,16,FThe Lady Chief Justice added: "We
OL,17,Frecord this was a double murder of
OL,18,Fspouses in the cruellest of
OL,19,Fcircumstances.
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOUvD@MO]xD@_OU
