OL,6,F"Our overall view is that the sentence
OL,7,Fwas neither wrong nor manifestly
OL,8,Fexcessive.
OL,10,F"We refuse leave to admit the new
OL,11,Fevidence or to extend time as we are
OL,12,Fnot convinced the new evidence
OL,13,Festablishes a valid ground of appeal.
OL,15,F"We are similarly not convinced that a
OL,16,Ffulsome enough explanation why this
OL,17,Fevidence was not produced earlier has
OL,18,Fbeen provided.
