OL,6,F"She engaged with the criminal justice
OL,7,Fagencies in an open and transparent
OL,8,Fmanner to present as a victim of
OL,9,Fcriminality.
OL,11,F"She made her case to a specialist
OL,12,Fabuse unit of the PSNI to allege that
OL,13,Fshe was drugged, sexually and mentally
OL,14,Fabused and raped by Colin Howell.
OL,16,F"For that she is to be commended in
OL,17,Ftaking the decision to come forward.
OL,18,FIt wasn't taken lightly."
